      "width": 189.15377807617188,
      "height": 140,
      "text": "Benchmarks to watch\n\nConnect accept:   30–40%\nReply rate:       10–15%\nMeeting booked:   3–5%\nSME sales cycle:  < 30 days\nEnterprise cycle: 90–270 days\nTrack: CAC · win-rate · NRR",
